About PetRehomer
We’re reimagining how you can responsibly rehome and adopt pets in the UK. PetRehomer has been created by Charity Buddy, a registered animal welfare charity no. 1189284, that believes it is time to make pet rehoming and adoption better for pets, great for people, and safer for everyone. Together, we can responsibly rehome pets within the UK using a better, kinder adoption process.
